{"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"update","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this method to update the appearance of the user location annotation. This"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method is called by the associated map view when it has determined that the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"user location annotation needs to be updated. This can happen in response to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"user interaction, a change in the user’s location, when the user tracking mode"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"changes, or when the viewport changes."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"During user interaction with the map, this method may be called many"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"times to update the user location annotation. Therefore, your implementation of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this method should be as lightweight as possible to avoid negatively affecting"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"performance."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"text":"Updates the user location annotation.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocationannotationview\/update"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView"]]},"sections